Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.81,0:01:29.92,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)\a6}製作 ？ 秋月暮葉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.53,0:01:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.56,0:01:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚者們的鄉愁 Part.2
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.35,0:01:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從道路的遠處有人會來迎接我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.60,0:01:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了 Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.51,0:01:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.83,0:02:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上有人通報
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.98,0:02:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一個孩子找不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.74,0:02:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Joaquin Sanchez
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.79,0:02:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像還偷了我的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.92,0:02:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事可以讓警察插手嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被問起販賣兒童的事情來就完蛋了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.63,0:02:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點去找！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.01,0:02:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用去工作嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.84,0:02:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.89,0:02:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在播這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你賭哪一邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.14,0:03:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是牛？ 還是Marco？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.19,0:03:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.99,0:03:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.23,0:03:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老太婆！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.77,0:03:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫為什么把Hatchin趕出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什么傻話！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.57,0:03:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連個招呼都不好好打 就把孩子丟下？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 這就是對家長的招呼嗎 Michiko
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.21,0:03:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰是誰的家長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 Michiko
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.68,0:03:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你身體長大了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.98,0:03:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我看來你還只是個乳臭未干、流著鼻涕的小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.78,0:03:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為你 Hatchin被Fantasma的人帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Sirkov 3世一口氣沖過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.83,0:04:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}露出破綻的Marco
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.49,0:04:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}能從這個困境中脫離嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.86,0:04:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}好！ Marco上前了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}成功了！ Marco
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.25,0:04:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}非常精彩的干掉了Sirkov 3世
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 大媽 是你的情郎嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她要是有個三長兩短我饒不了你！ 給我記住死老太婆！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.28,0:04:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡管來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.01,0:04:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么會把那個孩子丟給我？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“不能相信我嗎？”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.61,0:04:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是讓我相信你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.80,0:04:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了這個歲數我才意識到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說這種話的人 她的心情是不會假的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.92,0:04:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我被騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就祈禱她不會出事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.66,0:05:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則你就等著坐超特快列車下地獄吧！ 死老太婆！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.88,0:05:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Atsuko
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.60,0:05:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yolanda被你賣了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.50,0:05:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣到哪里去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對是在騙人！ 賣到很慘的地方去了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.68,0:05:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把老太婆你的錢去送給Yolanda 有什么錯！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.89,0:05:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 Michiko
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.01,0:06:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就那么不值得信任嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.62,0:06:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會信！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.19,0:06:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕是一點點也好 不能相信我一下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.00,0:06:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這樣的貪婪老太婆 坐超特快列車下地獄吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.64,0:06:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個混蛋！ 臭老太婆！ 臭老太婆！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我 老太婆！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.35,0:06:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.42,0:06:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差點以為自己要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.73,0:06:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么來找我？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.72,0:06:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 腿好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.14,0:06:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 還給我！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭個屁啊 是男孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.76,0:06:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 就這么一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.69,0:06:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈 沒膽魄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.02,0:06:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個還給你 好了吧 這樣可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能相信我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.37,0:07:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我也是人 討厭悲傷的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.19,0:07:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快點站起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.46,0:07:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想進來的話 就微笑著對我說對不起 這就是條件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.66,0:07:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個家伙抓住了Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.62,0:07:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道Fantasma的據點在哪里吧 能告訴我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.86,0:07:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 Ivan
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.21,0:07:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過的話 你好好聽了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.94,0:08:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來你一個人怎么去？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘍羅有一堆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了之后就 呯！ 呯！ 呯！ 被打成蜂窩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.21,0:08:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那個孩子不會有事的 暫時還死不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.53,0:08:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你去之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.90,0:08:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 Fantasma的據點我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.97,0:08:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來只要你大搖大擺宣揚自己是Michiko
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方會主動找上門吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.68,0:08:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 開玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.35,0:08:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過要下手的話就選明天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marco會和Roman 4世戰斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個孩子如果是對方的王牌的話 我們也必須有王牌在手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.36,0:08:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的老大你還記得嗎？ Vasili Nabokov
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiril疼愛過的跑腿小伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.45,0:08:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒有印象
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記好 長發的胖子 去找長發的胖子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天他一定會去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.76,0:09:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 約定好的事情 微笑著說對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.05,0:09:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？ 什么？ 完全聽不到嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.96,0:09:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 就這樣算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也行 就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.01,0:09:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}福利機構里的孩子們 還有從幼年起就支持著他的恩師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.42,0:09:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}背負著他們的寄托 Macro面對著明天的決戰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}直到現在依然在默默關注他的Seria Bastos女士說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}請... 請加油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.72,0:09:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.83,0:09:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 沒什么 只是很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.05,0:09:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.26,0:10:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.24,0:10:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要有欣賞玫瑰芬芳的從容
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.10,0:10:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般斗牛的肉都硬邦邦的不好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.93,0:10:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過Sirkov 3世
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是好吃到讓人流淚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 你是那個女人的什么人？ 女兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.49,0:10:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.71,0:10:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko Malandro... Michiko Malandro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.22,0:10:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.59,0:10:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.39,0:10:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.74,0:10:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana Morenos
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.37,0:10:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Morenos？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.82,0:10:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi Morenos的什么人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.27,0:10:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是他的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:11:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 他不是很久以前就死了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.40,0:11:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.95,0:11:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 是嗎 女兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.32,0:11:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉為什么這么好吃啊 真是不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.21,0:11:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 Hanamore
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.43,0:11:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana... more...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.34,0:11:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko會來救你吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很看重伙伴 我是這樣認為的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.50,0:11:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vasili先生 電話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.64,0:11:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Satoshi先生的電話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.46,0:11:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死胖子！ 你搞什么！ 耍我嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.53,0:11:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的Fantasma的孝敬錢 一點影子也沒有嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么！ 想造反嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.98,0:11:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我們的斗牛接連失敗...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.06,0:11:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫 切成薄片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.51,0:11:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切成薄片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.33,0:11:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說培根 你不知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼吸很急促哦 在流肥油嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.12,0:12:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 明晚一定把錢準備好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是你自己說的 火腿！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.21,0:12:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 Michiko Malandro出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓我們去做掉她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.51,0:12:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為答謝 我會把一份禮物給和錢一起送去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮物？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.18,0:12:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:29.33,portugal,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,250)}三月30日 Vermelha的斗牛競技場
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.93,0:12:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前還未發現疑似Michiko的蹤影
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我睜大眼睛玩命的去找
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼已經運出 等錢到了就出發
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.14,0:12:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發時通知Satoshi那個SB
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.17,0:12:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狙擊準備完了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.19,0:12:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝消音器了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.15,0:12:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標是Marco 不要射偏了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.86,0:12:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}今天與會招來腥風血雨的魔牛Roman 4世對陣的是Marco
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.95,0:12:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}馬上 馬上就要開始了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.67,0:13:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜查！ 把后面打開！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.52,0:13:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我們是來賣東西的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.73,0:13:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 把許可證也拿出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ok
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里面黏糊糊的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失禮 我洗得很干凈的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.78,0:13:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.16,0:13:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個小鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.78,0:13:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.75,0:14:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了廚房 就裝成售貨員混進觀眾席
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.48,0:14:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.45,0:14:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.68,0:14:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 不要開槍！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ivan 蹲下！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.91,0:14:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓你蹲下！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.18,0:15:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko怎么樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.51,0:15:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到處都找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}啊 登場了 微笑的貴公子Marco
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.41,0:15:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}正在回應觀眾的歡呼聲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.83,0:15:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}今天戴了面罩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.87,0:15:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}在如此重要的一戰 竟然有這樣的演出
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.78,0:15:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}面罩是在藐視對手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}異常熱烈的歡呼聲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.88,0:15:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}從Marco的對面出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.01,0:15:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}是Roman 4世
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.85,0:15:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}這幅樣子 真的是牛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.56,0:15:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}沖過來了 Roman
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.13,0:15:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}躲過去了！ 躲過去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}好不容易閃躲過去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:15:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}啊 卑鄙！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}不過 乘機刺出
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.12,0:16:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}沒有插上 沒有插上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.30,0:16:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}真是太難看了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.25,0:16:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}面罩脫落了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.52,0:16:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}不是Marco... 女性
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.33,0:16:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}斗牛士是神秘女性
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.83,0:16:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}巨大的倒彩聲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自投羅網啊 Mchiko
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.97,0:16:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這里 瞄準斗牛士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.78,0:16:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}面對Roman
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}插上了 插上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.44,0:16:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.14,0:16:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}場內也響起了歡呼聲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.98,0:16:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}劍？ 這里要用劍嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}所以說外行讓人頭痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.82,0:17:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko呢？ Michiko！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.01,0:17:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解開繩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.33,0:17:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.78,0:17:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}她好像在不停地注意著什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.45,0:17:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}希望她能集中精力斗牛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.66,0:17:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}雖然不知道她是誰 這位女性的架勢有模有樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.46,0:17:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}跳起來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}踩在Roman身上 跳向觀眾席
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.60,0:17:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}跑到這里來 是放棄比賽了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次在這里打斗是100年前了 Michiko Malandro
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.82,0:17:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,100年前？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.28,0:17:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你穿越個屁啊 死胖子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.73,0:17:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什么 Vasili
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.50,0:17:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連點樣子都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.47,0:18:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴硬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.79,0:18:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑腿的Vasili小子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.68,0:18:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko очень хорошо(俄語：太棒了)！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.91,0:18:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}因為出現了奇異的來客 競技場內充滿了異樣的狂熱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}不過居然只拿著勺子就進場了...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.71,0:18:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Roman以勺子少女為目標一口氣沖了過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.71,0:18:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}勺子少女在逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.22,0:18:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們兩個在搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,до свидания (俄語：再見) Michiko！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.75,0:18:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分勝負了 Vasili
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.67,0:18:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin 在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.61,0:18:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在應該在去Satoshi那個SB那里的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.68,0:18:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.17,0:18:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.08,0:19:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在干什么 快點來救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.93,0:19:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 快點 救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.60,0:19:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.22,0:19:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上過去 快點逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.77,0:19:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么不老老實實地做人質啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.09,0:19:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.67,0:19:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.78,0:19:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 掉頭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.87,0:19:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.45,0:19:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin 站起來！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.63,0:19:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊！ 跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.53,0:19:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快溜 快溜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.23,0:19:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.83,0:20:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要做多余的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.89,0:20:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 Michiko... 死... 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.68,0:20:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.04,0:20:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}神秘的女性斗牛士救出了勺子少女
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.48,0:20:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}說起Macro被發現倒在休息室
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.75,0:20:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}全裸 昏了過去嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.98,0:20:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒機會坐了呢 通往地獄的超特快列車
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,0:20:33.25,portugal,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}三月31日
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.74,0:20:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的要去見Satoshi？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.48,0:20:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.89,0:20:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoshi在Ossan
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.11,0:20:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過因為樹敵太多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以潛伏在地下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.32,0:20:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.26,0:20:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:20:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可別死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.14,0:21:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待續
